# VS Code REST Client or IntelliJ HTTP client format

### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Add person
POST http://localhost:3000/api/people
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Keanu Reeves",
  "born": 1964
}

### Add movie
POST http://localhost:3000/api/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Matrix",
  "released": 1999
}

### Create ACTED_IN
POST http://localhost:3000/api/acted-in
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "personName": "Keanu Reeves",
  "movieTitle": "The Matrix",
  "roles": ["Neo"]
}

### List people
GET http://localhost:3000/api/people?search=Keanu

### List movies
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies?search=Matrix

### Graph
GET http://localhost:3000/api/graph?limit=50

### GraphQL: people
POST http://localhost:3000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query($q:String){ people(search:$q){ name born actedIn{ title released } } }",
  "variables": { "q": "Keanu" }
}

### GraphQL: movies
POST http://localhost:3000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ movies{ title released actors{ name } } }"
}

